201
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:38,600
We want to swim, and you can't stop us!

202
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:55,400
Get out, or I will get in this pool and just grab you. Get out!

203
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:03,200
Get over here.

204
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:06,500
