224
00:14:31,500 --> 00:14:33,800
He wanted to stay in L.A., but there were too many memories.

225
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:36,800
He's renting for tax purposes, but he hopes to buy a place real soon.

226
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:38,300
