236
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:03,200
I don't want to talk to you about my love life anymore. It weirds me out.

237
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:05,500
I wouldn't have said anything. It's just...

238
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:07,500
What?

239
00:15:07,500 --> 00:15:11,500
I heard dad's girlfriend ask if you'd dated anyone since the divorce,

240
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:14,500
and dad said he doubted it.

241
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:18,700
And then they both laughed.

242
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:35,400
- Susan.
- Hi, Mike.

243
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:37,900
