284
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:05,300
And I really hate that I spend $15,000

285
00:18:05,300 --> 00:18:07,800
on your diamond necklace that you couldn't live without,

286
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:10,000
but I'm learning to deal with it.

287
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:12,800
So can I tell Tanaka we'll be there tomorrow night?

288
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:15,800
John. We have bandage stop shelf in the kitchen.

289
00:18:17,100 --> 00:18:20,100
Thanks, mrs. Solis.

290
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:24,600
Fine. I'll go.

291
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:27,700
