344
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:41,300
Mom!

345
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:44,300
Not now, honey. Mommy's threatening daddy.

346
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:47,400
Mom. No, I -- where are your brothers?

347
00:21:48,300 --> 00:21:51,300
- Noodles.
- My favorite.

348
00:21:56,700 --> 00:21:58,200
Lynette Scavo?

349
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:59,200
Crap.

350
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:02,200
Natalie Klein. I don't believe it.

351
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:05,200
Lynette. How long has it been?

352
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:07,400
Years.

353
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:09,000
Uh, how are you? How's the firm?

354
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:12,000
Good. Everyone misses you.

355
00:22:12,300 --> 00:22:14,200
Yeah. We all say if you hadn't quit,

356
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:15,800
