385
00:23:54,800 --> 00:23:56,900
You're right.

386
00:23:56,900 --> 00:23:59,400
So is that your project for school?

387
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:02,400
You know, when I was in fifth grade, I made the white house out of sugar cubes.

388
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:04,200
Stop stalling and go

389
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:07,000
