390
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:10,000
Tell me again why I fought for custody of you.

391
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:13,200
You were using me to hurt dad.

392
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:14,800
Oh, that's right.

393
00:24:17,300 --> 00:24:18,300
Oh, god.

394
00:24:26,100 --> 00:24:29,100
- Hi.
- Hey, Susan.

395
00:24:29,500 --> 00:24:32,400
- Are you busy?
- No, not at all. What's up?

396
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:35,600
Well, I -- I just, uh, was wondering if, um...

397
00:24:37,300 --> 00:24:40,200
if there was any chance that you, uh...

398
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:45,900
I-I just wanted to ask if...

399
00:24:46,700 --> 00:24:48,700
- Edie.
- Hey there, Susan.

400
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:49,700
What are you --

401
00:24:49,700 --> 00:24:52,000
I was making ambrosia, and I made too much,

402
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:55,000
so I thought I'd bring some over to mike.

403
00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:56,700
What's going on?

404
00:24:56,700 --> 00:24:59,800
