405
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,500
I have a clog.

406
00:25:06,500 --> 00:25:09,100
- Excuse me?
- And you're a plumber, right?

407
00:25:09,100 --> 00:25:10,600
Yeah.

408
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:12,300
The clog's in the pipe.

409
00:25:12,300 --> 00:25:14,800
Yeah, that's usually where they are.

410
00:25:14,800 --> 00:25:16,800
Well, I've got one.

411
00:25:16,800 --> 00:25:18,100
Oh, okay. Well, uh let me get my tools.

412
00:25:18,100 --> 00:25:20,400
Now? You want to come over now?

413
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,900
You have company.

414
00:25:21,900 --> 00:25:24,600
I don't mind.

415
00:25:24,600 --> 00:25:27,600
Yeah, just give me two minutes.

416
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:39,000
I'll be right over. That's it. Just stuff the hair down there.

417
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:42,000
I stuffed it. It's not enough to clog it.

418
00:25:43,500 --> 00:25:46,500
Here. Okay, look. Put in this peanut butter

419
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:49,600
