461
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:37,500
- With -- with onions?
- What?

462
00:28:37,500 --> 00:28:39,100
You put onions in my salad.

463
00:28:39,100 --> 00:28:42,100
No, I didn't.

464
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:47,800
Oh, wait.

465
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:56,400
The sound that awakened my son

466
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:59,200
