467
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:02,200
many years ago when he was quite young,

468
00:29:04,500 --> 00:29:07,500
but he recognized it instantly.

469
00:29:14,300 --> 00:29:17,300
It was the sound of a family secret.

470
00:29:34,700 --> 00:29:36,900
Seven days after my funeral,

471
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:39,900
life on Wisteria lane finally returned to normal,

472
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:44,700
which, for some of my friends...

473
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:47,700
was unfortunate.

474
00:29:49,800 --> 00:29:51,000
Now what?

475
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:54,000
Daddy's home!

476
00:29:56,300 --> 00:29:59,300
