552
00:36:10,100 --> 00:36:13,100
if you know what I mean.

553
00:36:13,600 --> 00:36:16,600
Oh, here's some antacid. Have you ever tried this?

554
00:36:18,100 --> 00:36:19,400
I can't believe it.

555
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:23,400
