595
00:40:11,200 --> 00:40:15,200
Life was suddenly full of... possibilities.

596
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:24,100
Not to mention a few unexpected surprises.

597
00:40:30,300 --> 00:40:31,600
Hello? Hey, it's me.

598
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:33,300
