605
00:40:55,700 --> 00:40:58,800
and what was left of my life.

606
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:02,300
All right, ladies, lift 'em up.

607
00:41:02,300 --> 00:41:03,500
To Mary Alice --

608
00:41:03,500 --> 00:41:05,500
